info.description:
Complete API collection for the CodeShack backend with sample data for testing.

## Real-Time Features (Socket.IO)

### Connection
```javascript
const socket = io('http://localhost:5000');
```

### Comment Events
- `join-doubt` - Join a doubt room to receive real-time comments
- `leave-doubt` - Leave doubt room
- `new-comment` - Emitted when new comment is created
- `comment-deleted` - Emitted when comment is deleted

### Junior Space Events
- `join-junior-space` - Join junior space to receive real-time posts
- `leave-junior-space` - Leave junior space
- `new-post` - Emitted when new post is created
- `post-deleted` - Emitted when post is deleted

### Example Usage
```javascript
// Join doubt discussion
socket.emit('join-doubt', doubtId);
socket.on('new-comment', (comment) => {
  console.log('New comment:', comment);
});

// Join junior space
socket.emit('join-junior-space');
socket.on('new-post', (post) => {
  console.log('New post:', post);
});
```

